{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a3f8c2e1-9b4d-4f6a-8c1e-2d5b7e904f31",
    "name": "Crypto Backtester API (Phase 4 / 4b)",
    "description": "Phase 4c REST + replay WebSocket v2.\n\n**Setup**\n1. `cd backend && docker compose up -d && python run_sync.py --backfill`\n2. `cd backend && python -m api` (default http://localhost:8000)\n3. Import this collection (variables are pre-filled)\n\n**Suggested order**\n1. Meta → Symbols → Chart Data (or Candles + Indicators)\n2. Users → Watchlists\n3. Replay REST session → WebSocket\n\n**Variables auto-set by tests:** `user_id`, `watchlist_id`, `session_id`\n\n**Timestamps:** Unix seconds UTC. Defaults: 2024-01-01 → 2025-01-01.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8000" },
    { "key": "wsBase", "value": "ws://localhost:8000" },
    { "key": "symbol", "value": "BTC/USDT" },
    { "key": "timeframe", "value": "1d" },
    { "key": "from_ts", "value": "1704067200" },
    { "key": "to_ts", "value": "1735689600" },
    { "key": "user_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "watchlist_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "session_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
