          "name": "Delete replay session",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/replay/sessions/{{session_id}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "08 Replay (WebSocket)",
      "description": "WebSocket v2 — connect after **Create replay session** sets `session_id`.\n\n**URL:** `ws://localhost:8000/ws/replay/{{session_id}}`\n\nOn connect: `replay_state` then `snapshot`. Client owns playback clock (`intervalMs = max(50, 1000/speed)`).\n\n**Refill tick queue:**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"refill\"}\n```\n\n**Step 1 bar:**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"step\", \"count\": 1}\n```\n\n**Play (sends tick_batch):**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"play\", \"speed\": 2.0}\n```\n\n**Pause:**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"pause\"}\n```\n\n**Seek:**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"seek\", \"to\": 1706745600}\n```\n\n**Change speed:**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"set_speed\", \"speed\": 5.0}\n```\n\n**Replace indicators (buffer_reset + snapshot):**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"set_indicators\", \"indicators\": [{\"key\": \"RSI\", \"params\": {\"period\": 14}}]}\n```\n\n**Get state:**\n```json\n{\"action\": \"get_state\"}\n```\n\n**Server events:** `replay_state`, `snapshot`, `tick_batch`, `buffer_loading`, `buffer_ready`, `buffer_reset`, `replay_completed`, `error`\n\nStep timeframe is fixed at session create (no mid-session TF change).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Connect replay WebSocket",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{wsBase}}/ws/replay/{{session_id}}",
              "protocol": "ws",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "8000",
              "path": ["ws", "replay", "{{session_id}}"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
